  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "The gym buzzes with chatter and flashing company logos. Rows of booths
    line the walls \u2014 tech firms, banks, NGOs \u2014 each with smiling recruiters
    and stacks of flyers. Alex clutches her folder of r\xE9sum\xE9s, trying to steady
    her nerves.\r\n\r\nThe air smells faintly of coffee and ambition. Everywhere
    she turns, someone\u2019s introducing themselves, handing out calling cards,
    talking about \u201Ccareer paths.\u201D She walks slowly through the crowd, the
    future suddenly feeling real \u2014 close enough to touch, but still a little
    out of reach.\r\n\r\nFor the first time, Alex isn\u2019t just a student \u2014
    she\u2019s a soon\u2011to\u2011be professional, ready or not"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 75a7dcceb17caec49b06beab28e14a39, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -1582481626441873841, guid: 75a7dcceb17caec49b06beab28e14a39, type: 2}
