  m_text: "From the hallway, Alex catches sight of the bustling gym filled with colorful
    booths and lively chatter. Recruiters shake hands, students swap r\xE9sum\xE9s,
    and banners advertise opportunities that sound both exciting and intimidating.\r\nShe
    pauses by the doorway, clutching her bag a little tighter. It\u2019s not her
    turn yet \u2014 but soon, it will be. The noise, the crowd, the future \u2014
    all waiting for her on the other side of those doors."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 75a7dcceb17caec49b06beab28e14a39, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -1582481626441873841, guid: 75a7dcceb17caec49b06beab28e14a39, type: 2}
